cast.overview: After experiencing a traumatic misfortune, Jasmine French, a wealthy woman from New York, moves to San Francisco to live with her foster sister Ginger and the firm purpose of getting a new life, but she will be haunted by anxiety and memories of the past.
cast.title: Blue Jasmine

details.biography: Andrew Long is a classically trained stage actor who is well known for many performances at the Shakespeare Theatre Company as well as notable roles at other local companies including Studio Theatre where he earned the Helen Hayes Award for Outstanding Actor in the searing drama Frozen.
details.name: Andrew Long
